result.name: Koon Thai Hai Nam Chicken

reviews.text:
Staffs, especially the cashier guy, are horrible and disgusting people.
Non-accomodative. Any kind of Food Service is Bad. 
Disrespecful People! They will make most foreign customer feels like its weighing them down to be a customer.

Will I reccomend it?
NOT! absolutely no.
I should make my self clear that its only the Sham Shui Po, Fuk Wing Street branch thats bad. 
Other branches must be okay.

Good value for your money. We ordered a meal for 4. We had 5 persons, but the food given was so much that we needed to take home some of the food. Customer service, on the other hand, was average. Otherwise, i would have it a 5 stars.
Ordered the Thai Laksa..quite tasty and its reasonably priced, Im likely recommending it to my friends.

Food was ordinary, services were terrible. Witnessed two female waiters (one looked like a boss) badly bullied an elderly male waiter, made my dinner very unpleasant! feel sorry for the old guy. Definitely won't go there again!!!
Offer tea set on holidays as well
